Package: fastknnumap
Type: Package
Title: Fast UMAP from Precomputed KNN Matrices
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Stefano User
Maintainer: Stefano User <stefano@example.com>
Description: A compact UMAP implementation focused on fast embeddings from
    precomputed nearest-neighbor index and distance matrices. The graph
    construction, exact nearest-neighbor search, and stochastic layout
    optimization are implemented in C++.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    Rcpp
Suggests:
    Rnanoflann,
    cluster,
    testthat,
    umap,
    uwot
LinkingTo:
    Rcpp
SystemRequirements: C++17
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
